        {
            "title": "迪士尼同意向OpenAI投資10億美元並達成授權協議",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 華特迪士尼公司同意向OpenAI投資10億美元，並將米老鼠、灰姑娘等其標志性角色授權給OpenAI人工智能短視頻平台。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據迪士尼周四發布的一份聲明，作為這項為期三年的授權協議的一部分，Sora將被允許使用迪士尼、漫威、皮克斯和星球大戰動畫與角色庫素材，根據用戶指令生成短視頻，這些視頻可供粉絲觀看和分享。該協議不包括任何演員肖像或聲音的使用。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">迪士尼將成為OpenAI的重要客戶，可以使用其人工智能工具打造新產品和體驗，並為員工部署ChatGPT。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0f744694-66b4-3f5a-8d98-1b825654cf17-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">迪士尼執行長鮑勃·艾格在聲明中說：「人工智能的快速發展對我們的行業來說是一個重要時刻，通過與OpenAI的這次合作，我們將在尊重並保護創作者及其作品的前提下，借助生成式AI負責任地擴大我們故事敘述的觸達範圍。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Source: Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZHLvU9W2UxM7phdNmxZHLg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c49fd3198e65a7aefebaa4bf7f6fb806\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Source: Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Disney Invests $1 Billion in OpenAI, Strikes Licensing Deal</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
